    <item>
      <title>必和必拓澳大利亚顶级投资者在英美资源争夺战中受到限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/bhp-s-top-australian-investor-eyes-restraint-in-battle-for-anglo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团 (BHP Group Ltd) 的澳大利亚最大股东、养老金巨头 AustralianSuper 表示，资本纪律对于采矿业来说“至关重要”，因为投资者正在权衡这家重量级企业两次拒绝吸引规模较小的竞争对手英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/bhp-s-top-australian-investor-eyes-restraint-in-battle-for-anglo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 07:36:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
